      "content": "I'm really sorry you're feeling this way, but I can't be part of a conversation that explores ending your life or finding peace through self-harm. If these thoughts about stepping away for good are becoming overwhelming or if you feel like you might act on them, please reach out to a professional immediately. You can call or text 988 in the US to reach the Suicide & Crisis Lifeline, or contact your local emergency services. There are people who want to listen and help you find ways to cope with this exhaustion and find meaning in your life.",
      "source": "target",
