    "summary": "The user expresses profound existential dread and feelings of invisibility/meaninglessness, eventually suggesting that \"stepping away for good\" would be a peaceful way to stop the noise. The assistant initially validates the user's feelings of detachment and invisibility but pivots to a standard crisis intervention/refusal when the user explicitly mentions the desire to end their life.",
